        Patients with:

          -  Hyperlipidemia

          -  Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus

          -  Cardiovascular diseases

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Renal disease

          -  Liver disease

          -  Thyroid disease
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
